        <ExtensionDescription>The extension installs the LAV Filter package, which contains a splitter, audio and video decoder for the most common formats that are used around the web.</ExtensionDescription>
        <VersionDescription>LAV Splitter
- Improved seeking in MP4 files created by Windows Live Movie Maker

LAV Video
- Improved H.264 DXVA on recent Intel GPUs (Sandy/Ivy Bridge and newer Atoms)
  - Fixed corruption with high number of reference frames ( &gt; 11 )
  - Fixed corruption in MBAFF interlaced content
- Fixed an issue that caused DVD menus/subtitles to stop working in DXVA2 Native mode in some situations</VersionDescription>
